  keywords = {android app,augmented reality,developed in the past,diagnostic and operative techniques,everal techniques have been,external ventricular drain,image-guided surgery,neuronavigation,of external ventricular drain,to improve the accuracy},
  pmid     = {26654178},
  review   = {Used an android app (Sina) to aid in freehand external ventricular drain (EVD) placement in 5 patients.

